# Project Report

   ## Title
   MOSFET Amplifier Simulation using Python

   ## Author
   Your Name Here

   ## Description
   This project simulates a Common Source MOSFET Amplifier.
   It covers DC biasing, Q-point calculation, voltage gain,
   and ID vs VDS characteristic curves.

   ## Files
   - simulations/ — Python simulation scripts
   - theory/      — MOSFET theory and design notes
   - graphs/      — Auto-generated simulation graphs
   - utils/       — Constants and helper functions

   ## How to Run
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   python main.py

   ## Status
   🚧 Report in progress — PDF will be added soon
